creator: Network Scanner - WiFi Scanner & Network Monitor
descriptionHtml:
The WiFi Router Warden - WiFi Analyzer app is useful WiFi Tools such as WiFi Detector, WiFi Analyzer, Detecting Who is on My WiFi, WiFi Signal Strength Meter, WiFi Signal and WiFi Channel Assessment etc.

The WiFi Analyzer & WiFi Blocker app is Powerful WiFi Protector to Detect Who is on my WiFi and Block strange devices to protect my WiFi Security. It is a super and free WiFi Blocker and WiFi Analyzer tool.

Features：
★WiFi Detector(Who is On My WiFi)★
WiFi Router Warden - WiFi Analyzer & WiFi Blocker app can easily scan my WiFi and find all devices connected to my WiFi network.
It can help you Block strange devices to protect my WiFi security or you can check the device and mark familiar devices as known..

★WiFi Analyzer
The WiFi Analyzer & WiFi Blocker app helps check your WiFi network by examining surrounding WiFi networks, measuring their signal strength as well as identifying crowded channels.

★WiFi Signal Strength
The WiFi Signal Analyzer app can tell you WiFi signal strength around you and see Which WiFi signal is better.

★WiFi Channel Assessment
The WiFi Analyzer tool shows the WiFi channels around you. It can help you to find a less crowded channel for your WiFi router.

★WiFi Signal Strength Meter
The WiFi Signal Strength Meter can detect WiFi Signal Strength around you in real time.
The WiFi Signal Meter can quickly check your WiFi strength to help you find the best location.

★Router Passwords
The WiFi Router App can help you discover the default keys and passwords of your WiFi Router.

Do you want to know analyze my WiFi easily? You just need to start WiFi Router Warden - WiFi Analyzer & WiFi Blocker and it will help you!
descriptionShort: WiFi Analyzer and WiFi Blocker to analyze my WiFi and Protect my WiFi Security.

★WiFi Detector(Who is On My WiFi)★
WiFi Router Warden - WiFi Analyzer & WiFi Blocker app can easily scan my WiFi and find all devices connected to my WiFi network.
It can help you Block strange devices to protect my WiFi security or you can check the device and mark familiar devices as known..

★WiFi Analyzer
The WiFi Analyzer & WiFi Blocker app helps check your WiFi network by examining surrounding WiFi networks, measuring their signal strength as well as identifying crowded channels.

★WiFi Signal Strength
The WiFi Signal Analyzer app can tell you WiFi signal strength around you and see Which WiFi signal is better.

★WiFi Channel Assessment
The WiFi Analyzer tool shows the WiFi channels around you. It can help you to find a less crowded channel for your WiFi router.

★WiFi Signal Strength Meter
The WiFi Signal Strength Meter can detect WiFi Signal Strength around you in real time.
The WiFi Signal Meter can quickly check your WiFi strength to help you find the best location.

★Router Passwords
The WiFi Router App can help you discover the default keys and passwords of your WiFi Router.

Do you want to know analyze my WiFi easily? You just need to start WiFi Router Warden - WiFi Analyzer & WiFi Blocker and it will help you!
